# Customer Support Ticket Management System

A full-stack support ticket platform designed to simulate real-world customer support workflows. Customers can raise tickets, track progress, communicate with agents, and receive updates — while admins manage assignments, workflows, and analytics.

---

## Overview

This application demonstrates a backend-focused architecture with clean API design, role-based access control, and structured workflows. The frontend is intentionally minimal but polished to reflect a modern support dashboard.

---

## Roles

Customer
- Create and view their own tickets
- Add comments to tickets
- Receive relevant notifications

Support Agent
- View assigned tickets
- Update ticket status
- Respond to tickets via comments

Admin
- Assign tickets to agents
- Manage the full ticket workflow
- Access the analytics dashboard

---

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL
- SQLAlchemy
- JWT Authentication

### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- Axios
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- Recharts

